reviews.review_text: No need to apologize or explain Not when this comes from Charlie Miller himself: "This looks like a superior transfer than my source, but it will obviously need to be pitch corrected to be at it's best. Hopefully someone (other than me) will take care of that."
Great Recording1 Great recording! This is even superior to Rob Bertrando's 8-5-71. This concert does take a backseat to 8-6-71....where Bertrando recorded a masterpiece.

Awesome for a '71 I don't like '71s, but this one is awesome. Would have to give it 4 stars were it not for the copious missing material. This recording sounds pretty warm & deep, & I like it better than the Miller, which doesn't usually happen. There are hot licks aplenty here. Download this one, or just listen to the matrix recording as a stream, as that sounds even better.
